From 389e143b5d81404afe543329b997647d2d5e0b90 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Adwait Nayak <adwaitn@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sun, 8 Jun 2025 14:40:45 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP: wifi: ath12k: Pending tasks for DP UMAC reset

Add support to enable UMAC SSR TLV debug stats
Add umac reset hw flag support for all 11BE chipsets
Add hw ring mask support for umac dp reset
Add DP umac reset interrupt support
Add bug fixes during umac reset

Below patchset was partially implemented as part of
0338-01-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-DP-UMAC-Reset-support.patch,
Rest of the implementation is done in this patch:
800-wifi-ath12k-Add-UMAC-DP-reset-support.patch

Signed-off-by: Ramya Gnanasekar <rgnanase@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Adwait Nayak <adwaitn@qti.qualcomm.com>
